{"tid":721024,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【獲傑出年青偶像】期待攞金針獎 鄭欣宜︰我梗係想攞！","createTime":"2018-06-28T11:47:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-28T12:04:29.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2ba4f55ed3537fbd32e7310731a7a863157b0554","tid":721024,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T11:47:27.000Z","msg":"鄭欣宜、菊梓喬、胡鴻鈞等人，今日喺紅磡出席全球華語金曲獎記者會，眾人獲頒傑出年青/偶像獎項，大會仲頒發百年巨星紀念大獎畀今年60歲冥壽的陳百強，由他舅父姚德華及陳百強紀念館長謝敏潼代領。<br />\n<br />\n欣宜得獎當然開心，佢搞笑話：「太好喇，趁仲有少少青春剩，可以得到呢個獎，過多幾年可能冇資格攞！」31歲嘅欣宜，還說：「其實喺呢一行，好多歌手都係好細個入行，但係我算係遲入行做歌手，23歲先入行。」<br />\n<br />\n不過佢已經進軍紅館開騷，欣宜笑言：「係型嘅，我覺得喺音樂路嚟講，係好好彩。」欣宜坦言期待得女歌手獎，問佢可會期待得金針獎？佢話：「如果我可以喺呢行屹立不倒20幾年，我梗係想攞，我相信任何一個歌手話唔CARE，相信都係客氣嘅說話，因為除咗對自己嘅認同，亦都係對團隊係一個肯定。」<br />\n<br />\n菊梓喬性感出席，佢笑自己喜歡骨感，A4身材冇加工，胡鴻鈞在旁也不敢斜視，表示女仔講求內在美，問他較喜歡對方，還是欣宜或許廷鏗？他笑說：「我所有都鍾意，大愛唔分種族、性別。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/28/194709_58040657ace2f4e65fc0acb167d0b920.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F28%2F194709_58040657ace2f4e65fc0acb167d0b920.png&h=5b8bba5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180628/58374636\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180628%2F58374636&d=7euVI9lNcrrryKnQ5M9xm5ZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=70e19be7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180628%2F58374636&h=ee1e5889\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180628/58374636</a>"},{"pid":"b88b1e384e93689b34a7847e0edb42eb29af0c30","tid":721024,"uid":70391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T11:59:28.000Z","msg":"依三個都可以拎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f34981a3c34703718410b4db47d67506139576d0","tid":721024,"uid":161990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T11:59:38.000Z","msg":"講還講"},{"pid":"5dde8c2982e181b824bc03f7cfd8c808a72ab90d","tid":721024,"uid":81562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T12:00:28.000Z","msg":"欣宜post真心唔洗有圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"637eb4bf38ee84dcdcae8160901425853ee7df1c","tid":721024,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5dde8c2982e181b824bc03f7cfd8c808a72ab90d","tid":721024,"uid":81562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T12:00:28.000Z","msg":"欣宜post真心唔洗有圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T12:04:29.000Z","msg":"放心 一定有"}]}